Package: longread-sc-visualization
Type: ShinyApp
Title: A Long-read Single-cell Visualization Application
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sefi Prawer
Maintainer: Sefi Prawer <sefi.prawer@unimelb.edu.au>
Description: This Shiny app allows users to upload Seurat objects and GTF files, and visualize gene and isoform expression in single-cell RNA-seq data.
